abstract: Samuel Smalley’s debut puzzle makes for a wild ride!
snippet: Samuel Smalley’s debut puzzle makes for a wild ride!
lead_paragraph: SATURDAY PUZZLE — Friends, I just took a week off from everything, including solving crosswords, and I … could not get anywhere with this grid, even after multiple attempts. Does rust form that quickly? I like to think that this puzzle is just tough as nails, and once I finally got my own claws into it I found it a terrific solve. The many, many trips I took through the clues also allowed me to better appreciate the eccentric wordplay and juxtapositions scattered throughout.
